Title: Mune: Guardian of the Moon
Writer: Benoît Philippon (original idea), Benoît Philippon (scenario), Benoît Philippon (adaptation), Jérôme Fansten (adaptation)
Actors: Omar Sy, Izïa Higelin, Michaël Grégorio, Shafik Ahmad
Plot: When an evil magma demon and his minions steals the sun of a magical world, the new guardians of both the sun and the moon must embark on a quest to retrieve it and save their world from disaster as the moon faces destruction as well.
